  h1 MOODI
  p.lead Application to help autistic kids deal with everyday conversation.
  hr
  .row
    .col-sm-6
      h2 Problem
      p For students with developmental disabilities that affect social interactions, sometimes the tone (or mood) of a person that is speaking to them is lost. At a liberal arts school like Penn State, students are encouraged to work and communicate with others in discussions and groups. Those with this disabilities often become isolated and have trouble working in those groups.
      p
