    .col-sm-6
      h2 Solution
      p Moodi is a mobile application for people that have trouble with social interactions. Using IBM’s Watson technology, Moodi takes speech, processes/analyses it, and lets the user know what the tone of the speech is. It will also be able to store those interactions for reference later by the user, or perhaps a parent or guardian for younger users. And have an easy interface to allow anyone to be able to use it.
      p
       // a.btn.btn-default(href='#', role='button') View details »
    .col-sm-6
      h2 Goals
      p Moodi will start as an android application with support for android wear. Eventually, Moodi has the potential to have its own hardware (the Moodi ring/bracelet), and be a multi-platform application.
      p
